From a90e9d84ec147be2ef6a720955f3b315cb54bca3 Mon Sep 17 00:00:00 2001
From: =?UTF-8?q?Dag-Erling=20Sm=C3=B8rgrav?= <des@des.no>
Date: Fri, 4 Oct 2024 17:45:58 +0200
Subject: [PATCH] Miscellaneous code cleanup (#2285)

This fixes various code quality issues I encountered while chasing a
memory leak reported by test automation. I failed to reproduce the
memory leak, but I hope you find this useful nonetheless.
